            <Label layoutX="30.0" layoutY="420.0" prefHeight="120.0" prefWidth="939.0" text="The RSA Cryptosystem - The RSA cryptosystem is one of the first public-key cryptosystems, based on the math of the modular exponentials and the computational difficulty of the RSA problem and the closely related integer factorization problem (IFP). The RSA algorithm is named after the initial letters of its authors (Rivest–Shamir–Adleman) and is widely used in the early ages of computer cryptography." wrapText="true">
